{
  "stem": "22892.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all night, we just-- we didn't-- nobody went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just all sitting up, waiting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, waiting to die, I guess, or-- what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the night, late at night, we saw activity like trucks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard the sound of trucks and, and lights of trucks, which normally you don't see over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think there were just no motorized vehicles there, except the lieutenant had a car and a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was trucks, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We heard that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, nobody said much of anything, because it's like, you know, you, you, you just don't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know you're waiting to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Early in the morning, it was-- start getting daylight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We saw the activity, and it was just getting so-- and I-- I walk out the door, and I say, like, I, I gotta run.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I started running down the hill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a road down the hill, and there were two policemen with rifles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were in uniform, and stopped me and pushed me back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's strange that I, I, I, I remember I smelled moonshine whiskey from these policemen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were like drinking all night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And here I'm back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was this open area on that huge farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, it's a big place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I got-- there was turmoil, women screaming, children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was like they can't find their children, running, looking for their husbands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it just-- it's just turmoil.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And running back and forth, and they surrounding the place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's already surrounded, most of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I came to an area with a huge fence, and I thought, boy, if I could break out that fence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It happened so that two adults did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
